{"tid":242343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友係郭靖 咁我係咩","createTime":"2017-05-13T21:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T13:24:29.000Z","uid":74214,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef0e31a86c80c8f10fd6c0279276a49949a452d","tid":242343,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T21:58:10.000Z","msg":"佢話自幼就對武術充滿興趣<br />\n睇金庸嘅書大 仲話黃榕係佢嘅理想型<br />\n男友為人俠義心腸 係路見不平會拔刀相助嘅好仔嚟<br />\n最近電視又播射鵰英雄傳<br />\n佢睇完話好想學武 鋤強扶弱<br />\n又話見到香港咁 好想練返一身好武功反共復華<br />\n咁佢就想學正宗少林拳<br />\n想問下各位巴打邊到有得學正宗少林拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有基督徒學少林拳有無衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申我係絲"},{"pid":"66aff2e9cb63e93a2fd5c4bdb316697bdfac9094","tid":242343,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T22:01:11.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"dad90c0b87878faba1760757ddbac07d22ed5ef5","tid":242343,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T22:07:33.000Z","msg":"乞衣雞"},{"pid":"47980f80c77c4d5f86184ee6aff7780ebfc4fe99","tid":242343,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T22:38:53.000Z","msg":"點解學武術都可以同宗教有衝突？"},{"pid":"e001efd3b424267eeac82b6e044209f542ae7fe0","tid":242343,"uid":70182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T22:55:20.000Z","msg":"你係華諍"},{"pid":"515b251965db00386d757b3419f329ea87f8adbb","tid":242343,"uid":70182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T22:56:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係華箏</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c3dba2bec2bc93b6928e3634f0c715e4719a8ccb","tid":242343,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T09:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乞衣雞</blockquote><br />\n第十九代丐幫幫主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3beddc7125cb2e076baaccd665ad40263836ba0d","tid":242343,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201